data.title: Andrea Stephenson - Women's Volleyball
data.meta_description:
Andrea Stephenson (9) Libero/Def. Specialist  - As a Senior (2018)
Academic All-MAC…Played in every match…Double-digit digs in nine matches, including a season-high
data.text:
As a Senior (2018)

Academic All-MAC…Played in every match…Double-digit digs in nine matches, including a season-high 18 against Western Illinois (Sept. 1)…17 digs against Western Michigan (Sept. 22), season-high against a MAC opponent…Recorded three service aces two times: against Ohio (Oct. 13) and Northern Illinois (Oct. 27).

As a Junior (2017)

Academic All-MAC...Appeared in 19 matches and 66 sets...Tallied 130 digs, ranking fifth on the team in digs per set (1.97)...10- plus digs in five straight matches (Oct. 14-28)…Registered six digs and one assist vs. Youngstown State (Sept. 16)...Notched 11 digs and three assists vs. Kent State (Oct. 14)…11 digs, two service aces against Eastern Michigan (Oct. 27)...Recorded 18 digs against Miami, a career high (Oct. 20)...Tallied 15 digs vs. Central Michigan (Oct. 28)...Had two kills- the first of her career- and nine digs at Buffalo (Nov. 4).

As a Sophomore (2016)

Earned spot on Academic All-MAC team...Appeared in 29 matches, playing 107 sets...Matched career high with three assists vs. Kent State (Oct. 15)...Ranked fourth on team with 1.79 digs per set ...Tallied 10 or more digs on seven occasions, including season-best 13 vs. Penn (Sept. 2).

As a Freshman (2015)

Saw action in 18 contests...Registered 1.64 digs per set...Tallied career-high 15 digs vs. Central Michigan (Nov. 13)...Notched 14 digs vs. Western Michigan (Oct. 2)...Collected nine digs at Buffalo (Sept. 26).

Prep

A 2015 graduate of East Kentwood High School...Four-year letterwinner in volleyball and was named to the all-academic team all four years...Accumulated 310 digs (2.4 digs per set) and 27 service aces...Earned three varsity letters in track and field...Named most valuable distance runner as junior and senior.

Personal

Born Andrea Rae Stephenson in Grand Rapids, MI...Daughter of Tom and Stephanie Stephenson... Has one brother, Trevor (16)...Majoring in business.
